1 (B) IN CONDUCTING THE RED LINE TRANSIT PROJECT, THE
2 ADMINISTRATION MAY NOT ACQUIRE ANY REAL PROPERTY FOR PLANNING,
3 CONSTRUCTION, OPERATION, OR MAINTENANCE OF THE RED LINE IF THE
4 ACQUISITION WOULD RESULT IN INVOLUNTARY RESIDENTIAL DISPLACEMENT.
5 SECTION 2. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act shall take effect July
6 1, 2025.

